  • Packages that use com.vmware.snapservice.tasks 
    Package Description

    The com.vmware.snapservice package provides interfaces for configuring and managing vSAN protection groups and snapshots
    com.vmware.snapservice.tasks
    The com.vmware.snapservice.tasks package provides interfaces to fetch general information regarding vSAN snapshot service tasks.
